                    "data"
                ],
                "summary": "getRasterData",
                "description": "This API allows programmatic access to an extensive collection of historical weather series covering the whole Italian territory with 10 km resolution, starting from 1961.\nIt allows to retrieve data contained within a time interval of interest and/or a geographical area of interest.",
